<div class="text-center">
    <h1 class="display-4">GameReady Tracker</h1>
    <p class="lead">Precise Health, Maximum Performance</p>
</div>

<div class="content-section">
    <h2>Sports' Biggest Problem: A Fan’s Perspective</h2>
    <p class="styled-text">Fans attend games with anticipation to witness their favorite stars in action. Imagine the disappointment when they discover their cherished players are sidelined.</p>
    <p class="styled-text">There exists a veil of secrecy around player injuries and load management, leaving fans in the dark.</p>
    <p class="styled-text">Unclear timelines compound the frustration, as fans are left uninformed about the progress players are making in their rest and recovery.</p>
</div>

<div class="content-section">
    <h2>Industry Need</h2>
    <p class="styled-text">The current recovery process is <b>inconsistent</b>, often dictated by player setbacks.</p>
    <p class="styled-text"><b>Player-specific</b> details significantly impact treatment protocols.</p>
    <p class="styled-text">Additionally, the <b>lack</b> of historical data on load management and recovery further compounds the challenges faced by the sports industry.</p>
</div>

<div class="content-section">
    <h2>Solution & Software Design</h2>
    <p class="styled-text">We propose the development of a cutting-edge software solution that empowers users to manipulate <b>historical data</b>, effectively tracking recovery and performance metrics.</p>
    <p class="styled-text">Our software aims to provide players with <b>realistic</b> timelines for rehabilitation and game readiness, based on comprehensive injury details and relevant variables.</p>
    <p class="styled-text">The ultimate goal is to <b>optimize</b> sports health, ensuring peak performance across the board.</p>
</div>

<div class="content-section">
    <h2>Vantage Point of the Customer</h2>
    <h3>Athlete:</h3>
    <p class="styled-text"><b>"Real-Time Map for the Player"</b></p>
    <p class="styled-text">Building confidence in injured athletes by providing transparent insights into their recovery journey.</p>
    <p class="styled-text">Ending the stigma surrounding certain "career-ending injuries" through informed and effective treatment plans.</p>
    
    <h3>Team:</h3>
    <p class="styled-text"><b>"Protecting their Best Assets"</b></p>
    <p class="styled-text">Offering valuable advice in constructing a contending roster by considering player-specific recovery needs.</p>
    <p class="styled-text">Building confidence in the roster created and providing an insurance policy for the capital invested in star players.</p>
</div>